@mm7700 This link will explain all my friend. Just go down to the burn section. Link : http://sharethefiles.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=24&t=192121

And.. when you get to actually burning the disc, click "trunicate" and not overburn. It will bring up a message saying that the game/file may be to big in size. Just hit "ok" to continue and BAM! You have a burned game :)

Btw, I have used 3 DVD+R DL memorax disc instead of verbatim and have burnt 3 flawless disc...
